snippet.title: Spanky! Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Spanky is THE booty-physics party game that brings cheeky movement mechanics to chaos-filled party modes. Twerk online with up to 7 friends and slap some jiggly tush!

WISHLIST NOW! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1732420/Spanky/

-

Thank you to everyone who has tagged along this journey. There is so much more to come.
Spanky is our first title as a dev duo and started out 3 years ago as a silly little prototype to learn game development. It's thanks to everyone following our progress that this has been possible, we hope you get to try Spanky and that it brings many of you some joy and stupid laughs. 

Cheers!
Rory - HappyHead Games CEO, Founder, Revolutionary Developer, Booty Enthusiast, Jiggle professor & Award-winning twerk coach.
